            "description": "### Description\nAuthenticate a user and retrieve a JWT access token.\n\n### Flow\n1. Client sends username (email) and password as form data.\n2. Server verifies credentials.\n3. Server issues a JWT signed with the secret key.\n4. **Postman Test Script**: Automatically extracts the `access_token` and saves it to the `{{token}}` collection variable for future requests.\n\n### Authentication\n* Not Required\n\n### Request Body\n* `username`: string (email)\n* `password`: string\n\n### Response\nReturns the access token and token type."
