            "description": "### Description\nCreate a new bookmark associated with the authenticated user.\n\n### Flow\n1. Validates the URL format.\n2. Saves the bookmark with the user's ID as the owner.\n3. Processes the `tags` array: finds existing tags or creates new ones tied to the user.\n\n### Authentication\n* Required: Bearer Token\n\n### Request Body\n* `title`: string (required)\n* `url`: string (required, valid URL)\n* `description`: string (optional)\n* `tags`: array of strings (optional)\n\n### Response\nReturns the created bookmark including embedded tag details."
